702002f-a.title: Bronx: Waldo Avenue - 238th Street (West)
702002f-a.text:
A panoramic view northeastward across the car yards of the
Interborough Rapid Transit Co., the elevated structure of the I.R.T.
Van Cortlandt Park subway and its 242nd Street station, on Broadway;
and Van Cortlandt Park, as seen from the N.E. corner of Waldo Ave. and
West 238th Street.
May 1926.
Brown Brothers.
